lead_paragraph: Former Baylor coach Art Briles tells a Waco television station that the school-commissioned report on its handling of sexual assault allegations has not been shared with him and that he assumes it supports a conclusion already drawn by the board of regents.

headline.print_headline: Report: Briles Says He Would Have Done Things Differently
